Third-party components
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

This application bundles prebuilt binaries of xdelta3, used for applying
binary delta patches during localization installation:

    internal/xdelta/resources/xdelta3.exe    (Windows)
    internal/xdelta/resources/xdelta3_linux  (Linux)
    internal/xdelta/resources/xdelta3_mac    (macOS)

